WEBVTT

00:04:59.960 --> 00:05:01.456
(Laughter)

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:04.896
Did you ever think to yourself,
"What is wrong with this picture?"

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:06.896
Well, what if the real question is,

00:05:06.920 --> 00:05:10.376
"What is wrong with the men
that designed these bathrooms?"

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:16.296
(Applause)

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:17.936
It may seem like a small thing,

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:20.680
but it's representative
of a much more serious issue.

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:25.976
The contemporary world
was literally built by men

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.096
who have rarely
taken the time to understand

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:31.416
how people unlike them